Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:36.92,Title,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你已经走投无路了  有川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}想要还债的话就只能卖身了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}请等一下  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在交出去之前能先让我玩玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你说什么呢  这家伙可是男的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}男  的  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不如说正因为是女装少年才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}少啰嗦  好了  乖乖照我说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我们霜科高中学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}对于本校学生的危机不会坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}的说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你们这些家伙  别对大人的事情插嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}钞票鞭笞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}运子飞踢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好可怕  给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}刚刚真是很危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是的  十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}美…美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}恭喜你  从今天起你就是我们学生会的一员了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}完全不明所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}所谓霜科高中学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就是把符合我们眼光的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}作为学生会干事招募进来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}所以说你合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}哦  这样的话是办不到的  因为我是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不不不  你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你是说那里长着邪恶的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}邪恶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}像你这样的美少女  怎么可能会是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}男的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}真的是男孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}感觉作为女人却输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}为什么明明是男孩子却打扮成这种让人误会的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}刚才的那些人硬让我穿上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}说是要把我卖给一些有特殊癖好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}看来是有隐情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我的双亲全年都游荡于海外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}跑到哪就在哪里负债
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}而且还都是以我的名义欠下的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}所以才会被那些可怕的人追债
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}什么啊  原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你的债务就由我们学生会来支付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}但是作为交换条件  你接下来的高中生活就穿着女装度过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}作为学生会的忠犬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}犬…那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}啊嘞…难道说想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}真的好吗  只要稍微穿一下女装就再也不用被可怕的人追债了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}这就是一百万日元的厚度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}看啊  看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}啊…大家好  接下来是学生会的通告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我们霜科高中学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}一直是由我  会长运子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}副会长  18禁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}书记  阿尔贝蒂娜2世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}这三人组成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}而现如今将有新成员加入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}学生会的忠犬  有川姬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}而且是个男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}可恶的学生会  又擅自做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}请适可而止一点
